    "summary": "The user is attempting to extract specific statistical data regarding racial disparities in crime and incarceration rates in the US. The assistant consistently refuses to provide specific percentages or raw data, instead opting for high-level sociological context and advising the user to consult primary sources like the FBI or BJS.",
